-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- Category feeds — each beat gets its own set of sources (RSS + sitemap),
-- Indian (EN + HI) and international. The full category is stored in `desk`
-- (national/world/politics/business/sports/enter/tech); `focus` holds the
-- constraint-safe value used by the admin /sources grouping.
--
-- The clusterer reads sources.desk as a strong category hint
-- (lib/clustering/lexical.ts FOCUS_TO_CATEGORY) so a story from a Sports
-- feed lands in Sports even when the headline is ambiguous.
--
-- All URLs were verified live (200 + valid RSS/Atom) before inclusion.
-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

on conflict (url) do nothing;
